{"word":"παραθέω","slug":"παραθέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>παραθέω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-θεύσομαι</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to run beside</i> or <i>alongside</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to run beyond, outrun</i>, <el>τινά</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>: <i>to run past</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><i>to touch on cursorily</i>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}